{
    "poem_title": "CELLE QUI CHANTAIT",
    "author": "Théodore de Banville",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1867",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Voix solitaire, ô délaissée !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Victime tant de fois blessée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Chère morte dont l'âme eut faim",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Et soif d'azur, ô Marceline,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Dors-tu, sous la froide colline ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "As-tu trouvé le calme, enfin ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voix solitaire, ô délaissée !\nVictime tant de fois blessée,\nChère morte dont l'âme eut faim\nEt soif d'azur, ô Marceline,\nDors-tu, sous la froide colline ?\nAs-tu trouvé le calme, enfin ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Quand, parmi la lente agonie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "La douleur, qui fut ton génie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "T'arrachait de tremblants aveux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Le souffle du maître farouche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "En passant déliait ta bouche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et frissonnait dans tes cheveux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quand, parmi la lente agonie,\nLa douleur, qui fut ton génie,\nT'arrachait de tremblants aveux,\nLe souffle du maître farouche\nEn passant déliait ta bouche,\nEt frissonnait dans tes cheveux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Pâle, vouée à ta chimère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Tes dents mordaient la cendre amère ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "T'en souvient-il, t'en souvient-il,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "À présent que tes yeux sans voiles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "S'emplissent de flamme et d'étoiles ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Tu n'acceptais pas ton exil !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pâle, vouée à ta chimère,\nTes dents mordaient la cendre amère ;\nT'en souvient-il, t'en souvient-il,\nÀ présent que tes yeux sans voiles\nS'emplissent de flamme et d'étoiles ?\nTu n'acceptais pas ton exil !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tu t'écriais, inassouvie :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "\" Amour ! Je veux, dès cette vie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ton délire immatériel",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et tes voluptés immortelles :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Puisque l'âme a gardé ses ailes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Il faut bien qu'on lui rende un ciel ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tu t'écriais, inassouvie :\n\" Amour ! Je veux, dès cette vie,\nTon délire immatériel\nEt tes voluptés immortelles :\nPuisque l'âme a gardé ses ailes,\nIl faut bien qu'on lui rende un ciel ! \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Non ! Tout désir qui nous déchire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "N'est qu'un avant-goût du martyre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Non, l'univers déshérité,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Où toute vertu saigne et pleure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ne peut pas nous donner une heure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Fût-ce au prix de l'éternité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Non ! Tout désir qui nous déchire\nN'est qu'un avant-goût du martyre !\nNon, l'univers déshérité,\nOù toute vertu saigne et pleure,\nNe peut pas nous donner une heure,\nFût-ce au prix de l'éternité."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Qu'importe ! Marchons vers le rêve.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "L'ange a beau secouer son glaive",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Sur le seuil que cherchent nos pas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Rôdons aux portes entr'ouvertes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Cherchons sur les cimes désertes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "La rose qui n'y fleurit pas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'importe ! Marchons vers le rêve.\nL'ange a beau secouer son glaive\nSur le seuil que cherchent nos pas,\nRôdons aux portes entr'ouvertes !\nCherchons sur les cimes désertes\nLa rose qui n'y fleurit pas !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Allons-nous-en vers le mirage !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Écoutons à travers l'orage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "La voix qui nous a désignés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Pour la félicité sereine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Et que l'ombre à la fin nous prenne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Vaincus, mais non pas résignés.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Allons-nous-en vers le mirage !\nÉcoutons à travers l'orage\nLa voix qui nous a désignés\nPour la félicité sereine,\nEt que l'ombre à la fin nous prenne,\nVaincus, mais non pas résignés."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Vous le savez, brises fécondes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Torrents qui roulez dans vos ondes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Une poussière d'astres clairs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Cascades qui volez en poudre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Sapins noirs brisés par la foudre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Rochers mordus par les éclairs !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous le savez, brises fécondes,\nTorrents qui roulez dans vos ondes\nUne poussière d'astres clairs,\nCascades qui volez en poudre,\nSapins noirs brisés par la foudre,\nRochers mordus par les éclairs !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Vous le savez ; et toi, nuit noire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Tu le vois, ce n'est pas la gloire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Que suit le poëte aux beaux yeux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Ce n'est pas pour elle, ô nature !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il verse à la race future",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Un flot de chant mélodieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous le savez ; et toi, nuit noire,\nTu le vois, ce n'est pas la gloire\nQue suit le poëte aux beaux yeux.\nCe n'est pas pour elle, ô nature !\nQu'il verse à la race future\nUn flot de chant mélodieux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Ce n'est pas lui qu'on rassasie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Avec cette vaine ambroisie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Et dédaigneux du laurier vert,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Au milieu de la multitude",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Il garde la morne attitude",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "D'un sphinx regardant le désert.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce n'est pas lui qu'on rassasie\nAvec cette vaine ambroisie ;\nEt dédaigneux du laurier vert,\nAu milieu de la multitude\nIl garde la morne attitude\nD'un sphinx regardant le désert."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Mais quand ses odes ingénues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Sur le front immense des nues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Devancent l'aigle et le vautour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "C'est qu'il dit à l'antre sonore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "La brûlure qui le dévore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Seulement altéré d'amour !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais quand ses odes ingénues\nSur le front immense des nues\nDevancent l'aigle et le vautour,\nC'est qu'il dit à l'antre sonore\nLa brûlure qui le dévore,\nSeulement altéré d'amour !"
        }
    ],
